      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Mystery Shrouded in Mist",
        "Client": "Slimy Researcher",
        "Description": "I was collecting Gore Magala\r\nscales for an experiment, but...\r\nIt all happened so quickly. I\r\nwas engulfed in mist, then\r\ncovered in strange slime-like\r\npoison. *shrug* Another day\r\nas a researcher, am I right?",
        "Target": "Slay a Chameleos and\r\nhunt a Gore Magala",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Myst\u00E8re et boule de gomme",
        "Client": "Chercheur v\u00E9reux",
        "Description": "Je collectionnais les \u00E9cailles\r\nde Gore Magala pour mes\r\nrecherches, mais tout est\r\nfini... Tout est all\u00E9 si vite.\r\nj\u0027ai \u00E9t\u00E9 submerg\u00E9 par la brume\r\net recouvert d\u0027un poison\r\ngluant. Tu dois me venger !",
        "Target": "Tuer un Chameleos et\r\nchasser un Gore Magala",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ricerca velata di nebbia",
        "Client": "Ricercatore viscido",
        "Description": "Stavo raccogliendo scaglie di\r\nGore Magala per un esperimento,\r\nma \u00E8 tutto finito. \u00C8 successo\r\ntutto cos\u00EC in fretta! Sono stato\r\navvolto dalla nebbia, poi sono\r\nstato ricoperto da uno strano\r\nveleno vischioso. Vendicami!",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Chameleos\r\ne caccia un Gore Magala",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Monster im Nebel",
        "Client": "Schleimiger Forscher",
        "Description": "Ich habe Gore-Magala-Schuppen\r\nf\u00FCr ein Experiment gesammelt,\r\naber... alles ging so schnell!\r\nPl\u00F6tzlich war ich in Nebel\r\ngeh\u00FCllt, dann voll schleimigem\r\nGift. Aber so ist es nun mal,\r\ndas Forscherleben, nicht wahr?",
